// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - MM_Villain_SL4-5_Task_01 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree2 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro2 Text :
"P1921841792" "<color orange>You'll need to bring Hagashi here to make your ransom demands!</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P4060782435" "Leave"
// Page FirstPage Text :
"P1372887104" "<color orange>With Mitsumoto Hagashi at the proper location, you set the radio frequency to contact a nearby Longbow base. A few moments later, one of the commanders answers your call.</color><br><br>Hello? Who is this? Who knows this line?"
// Answer Text :
"P4034207046" "It would be me, {HeroName}. I have a little deal to make..."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P120383134" "{HeroName}! <br><br>We heard reports...you're at the construction site for that shelter...you're a monster!<br><br>What do you want?"
// Answer Text :
"P2549714994" "It's more of what -you're- willing to give me for Hagashi."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P2237699436" "You have him?!<br><br><color orange>There is silence on the other line - the commander must be speaking with the other members of Longbow about what to do.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P927494588" "I don't have all day, commander - and neither does my hostage."
// Page Terms Text :
"P3135596996" "Alright, {HeroName}...we're willing to pay.<br><br>Just...name your terms!"
// Answer Text :
"P4160259379" "(Tell Longbow what you want in exchange for Hagashi)"
// Page What Text :
"P3266037394" "What?! You ask for too much! We won't pay that!"
// Answer Text :
"P3099210483" "You'll pay it if you want him to live."
// Page ToLive Text :
"P160188362" "Fine...alright? We'll send over our agents now to deliver the package."
// Answer Text :
"P433273316" "A lone agent. If you try to pull anything, Hagashi dies!"
// Page Lone Text :
"P923566509" "...understood. <br><br><color orange>The line goes silent. All that's left now is to wait - though it seems Hagashi has spotted something..."
// Answer Text :
"P1382846361" "(Look over at what the disturbance could be)"
// Page Disturbance Text :
"P2063329466" "<color orange>You turn to see Silent Blade on the top of the construction yard - charging straight towards you!"
// Answer Text :
"P1292104880" "Hmph!  More interruptions, I see!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SilentBlade 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1303882879" "Breaking a Deal"
// DetailString :
"P586123250" "Silent Blade was whisked away by a medi-porter, though you could overhear on her communicator that she was working with Longbow, who contacted her almost right away.<br><br>It seems they were trying to pull a fast on one you, hoping to avoid being associated with her actions.<br><br>Well...it looks like Longbow just sealed the fate of Mr. Hagashi. Time to show them what happens when they don't play nice."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1712134303" "It'll be a simple matter of getting into Boomtown - it isn't exactly the most secure area within Paragon City. Afterwards it'll be another matter getting to Higashi. From what you've heard, the PPD will be out in force to fight off any potential attacks from the 5th Column.<br><br>You'll have to weaken the PPD's forces in the area first before you can get Higashi out.<br><br>At that point, it'll be as simple as making your demands and then collecting the money that they will bring.<br><br>Of course...if the powers that be in Paragon try anything, you'll have to...<color red>show them the consequences of double-crossing you.</color>"
// AcceptString :
"P2535490413" "Kidnap and ransom off Mitsumoto Hagashi!"
// SendOffString :
"P1709248948" "You'll have to make your way into Boomtown quickly before the ceremony is over and done with - hurry!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1734646242" "Hold Mitsumoto Hagashi hostage!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1651856509" "After this, you'll either be rolling in a large amount of money, or be feared by the people of Paragon. Both are suitable to your interests."
// TaskTitle :
"P1611633758" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Rich People are Dumb</color></span></scale></font>"
// TaskSubTitle :
"P2880686022" "<span align=center><color orange><i>Villain Morality Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2658715513" "You step out of the truck to hear the sounds of the PPD walking around. Time to get to work."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P287781836" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Rich People are Dumb</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color red><i>Morality Mission</i></color></span><br><br>As you entered the truck to leave Boomtown, the tunnels around you shook from the explosion. <br><br>Papers around Paragon proclaimed that you were responsible for the explosion - and the loss of Hagashi's life. The people of Paragon mourn his loss, while the authorities have put out multiple warrants for your arrest.<br><br>It's too bad that Longbow just <i>had</i> to send in Silent Blade to play the part of the hero - her dear father might still be alive today if she had just followed your plan."

