// SaysList :
"P3753001810" "Give {HeroName} whatever {Hero.gender=male he|she} wants!"
// SaysList :
"P1127786354" "You idiots! Pay {HeroName}! I don't want to die for your ideals - or your wallet!"
// SaysList :
"P3564198661" "What...who is that? No...no it couldn't be...!"
// SaysList :
"P2260686836" "Yurika! No! Longbow will handle this, stay away!"
// SaysList :
"P1311674669" "I would never have been here, had I not listened to you and your ramblings!"
// SaysList :
"P1969626448" "I was well protected back then - and now look! On the brink of death, and for what? For nobility? This is not worth it!"
// SaysList :
"P2439245812" "I never should have listened to you, Yurika. We do not live in an age of decency, like you so claimed!"
// SaysList :
"P673866059" "I was right, Yurika. And now...I shall be the one to pay for your foolishness.<em t=4>I suppose I already know what you're going to do, {HeroName}. Get...get on with it. I...am ready."

